# CFP-2434 (Epic CFP-2418 deferred 배선 closure) — placement governance 게이트 2종
# (CFP-2422 L2 책임→레포 토폴로지 + CFP-2428 L1 코드→책임 marker drift) 의 full
# closure 등재. warning-tier(continue-on-error) → Tier2(functional, coe:true) 정합.
# whitelist(consumer_applicable_workflows.txt) += 2 basename 과 atomic 동일 PR
# (3-way gate AC-3). ADR-130 §결정3/5 closure-완전성: yml run-block 1-hop = .sh
# (ADR-061 thin wrapper), .sh→python3 lib/*.py = depth-2 SSOT → 둘 다 등재 의무.
# .sh = :dep_workflow 부착(신규 whitelist basename, 방향2 membership + degraded
#   suppression). .py = script-only(:dep_workflow 미부착 — 방향2 비대상 phantom 회피,
#   §결정3 closure-완전성으로 직접 등재). 4 asset 모두 chmod +x(100755) — Check 4
#   exec-bit 의무(.sh/.py 비면제, check-consumer-scripts-manifest.sh L137-148).
scripts/check-responsibility-topology.sh:templates/github-workflows/responsibility-topology-check.yml
scripts/lib/check_responsibility_topology.py
scripts/check-responsibility-marker-drift.sh:templates/github-workflows/responsibility-marker-drift-check.yml
scripts/lib/check_responsibility_marker_drift.py

# CFP-2451 (CFP-967 Phase 2 deferred wire 완성) — parallel-work sentinel 전파 closure.
# ADR-073 Amendment 2 §결정 1-A/1-B/1-C mechanical verification (CFP-953/CFP-946 2-incident
# sentinel) 의 consumer 전파. warning-tier(continue-on-error) → Tier2(functional, coe:true) 정합.
# parallel-work-sentinel-check.yml run-block 1-hop = .sh (ADR-061 thin wrapper),
# .sh→python3 lib/*.py = depth-2 SSOT(title-search/epic-state-poll/head-compare 3-mode 본체).
# whitelist(consumer_applicable_workflows.txt) += parallel-work-sentinel-check.yml 와 atomic
# 동일 PR (3-way gate 정합). ADR-130 §결정3/5 closure-완전성: 둘 다 등재 의무.
# .sh = :dep_workflow 부착(신규 whitelist basename, 방향2 membership + degraded suppression).
# .py = depth-2 closure asset — 동일 workflow run-block 1-hop exec(.sh→python3) 닫힘이라
#   :dep_workflow 부착(consumer degraded copy 시 .py 누락 hard-block 회피). 둘 다 chmod +x
#   (100755) — Check 4 exec-bit 의무(.sh/.py 비면제, check-consumer-scripts-manifest.sh L137-148).
scripts/check-parallel-work-sentinel.sh:templates/github-workflows/parallel-work-sentinel-check.yml
scripts/lib/check_parallel_work_sentinel.py:templates/github-workflows/parallel-work-sentinel-check.yml

# CFP-2506 (ADR-033 Amendment 1) — Rust consumer 로컬빌드 경로 표준.
# build-local.{sh,ps1} = consumer 가 자기 Rust repo 루트에서 한 줄 실행하는
# ad-hoc 개발자 CLI (cargo check 1차 → Docker 마운트 빌드 / native cargo →
# graceful degrade). CI runtime invoke 아님(workflow 가 호출하지 않음) →
# dependent-workflow 미부착 (codeforge-upgrade.sh 선례 답습). bootstrap-consumer.sh
# Stage 7 가 consumer repo 에 1:1 mirror → consumer 가 `templates/scripts/build-local.*`
# verbatim 경로로 접근. 둘 다 chmod +x(100755) — Check 4 exec-bit 의무(.sh/.ps1 비면제).
templates/scripts/build-local.sh
templates/scripts/build-local.ps1
